name: Black Hole Rush
summary: Black Hole Rush is a thrilling VR game where you must defend the universe from waves of enemies by sending them spiraling into a massive black hole. Utilize your skills and strategies to grab, push, or launch enemies into the void, all while avoiding their attacks. As the levels progress, the challenges become more intense, and only the quickest reactions can save the galaxy from destruction. Dive into the immersive chaos and control the power of the black hole!
